sub_title: Customer Success Manager at Akeneo | eCommerce | Future-Proof PIM & PXM
summary:
I enjoy to work in a supportive, collaborative work environment with international atmosphere. I am good at managing projects & people as I am very organized, efficient, dynamic and able to help people in any way. I am a good communicator and I can communicate well both in written and spoken in English, Finnish and Swedish. I am passionate about digital innovation and new technology and I love meeting new people and learning new things.

Connect with me over LinkedIn for networking, career opportunities, and more!
